<h2>Alege cei mai buni specialisti pentru promovarea cabinetului tau!</h2>
<div class='clearfix'></div>
<form class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="{USER_CREATE_LINK}" method='post'>
<div class='row well well-lg login_form'>
	<div class="help-block text-left">Pentru adaugarea unei firme trebuie sa va creati un cont. <a href="{CONTNOU}" target='_blank'>Exemplu creare cont nou</a></div>
	<div class='col-sm-7 col-xs-12 text-left'>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='firstname'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-pencil'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='firstname' class="form-control" placeholder="Numele dvs ..." value="{FIRSTNAME}" aria-describedby="firstname">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='lastname'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-pencil'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='lastname' class="form-control" placeholder="Prenumele dvs ..." value="{LASTNAME}" aria-describedby="lastname">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='email'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-envelope'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='email' class="form-control" placeholder="Adresa de email ..." value="{EMAIL}" aria-describedby="email">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='username'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-user'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='username' class="form-control" placeholder="Utilizator/ username ..." value="{USERNAME}" aria-describedby="username">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='pass_1'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-lock'></span></div>
				<input type="password" name="pass_1" class="form-control" placeholder="Parola dvs ..." value="" aria-describedby="pass_1">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='pass_2'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-lock'></span></div>
				<input type="password" name="pass_2" class="form-control" placeholder="Confirmati parola ..." value="" aria-describedby="pass_2">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='security'><img src="{SITE_BASE}/security_image.php?code={SECURITYID}" alt="Security Image"></div>
				<input type="text" name="security_code" class="form-control" placeholder="Cod ..." value="" aria-describedby="security">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				Sunt de acord cu <a href="{TERMENICONDITII}">termenii si conditiile</a> site-ului.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<input type="checkbox" name="agree" value="agree" checked>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<button type="submit" name="login" class="btn btn-info btn-lg">Trimite</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class='col-sm-5 col-xs-12 text-center'>
		<div class="help-block text-left">
			<p><u>Va rugam sa completati cu atentie campurile formularului.</u></p>
			<br>
			<p>Odata ce ati completat formularul si dati click pe "Trimite" deveniti membru al site-ului DentistOnline.ro si 
				 veti beneficia de anumite servicii, in functie de pachetul de promovare ales. </p>
		</div>
		<br>
		<p class="article_details_title"> Ai nevoie de ajutor?</p>
		<p class="help_phone">Ne puteti contacta de Luni-Vineri la numarul de telefon: <br><b>0727-380-368</b>.</p>
	</div>
</div>
</form>
